" (quotes, angle quotes, parentheses, etc)
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>" :<C-u>call <SID>RD_wrapper('"')<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>' :<C-u>call <SID>RD_wrapper("'")<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>` :<C-u>call <SID>RD_wrapper('`')<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>{ :<C-u>call <SID>RD_wrapper('{')<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>( :<C-u>call <SID>RD_wrapper('(')<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>[ :<C-u>call <SID>RD_wrapper('[')<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <Leader>< :<C-u>call <SID>RD_wrapper('<')<CR>
